data.title: The Vyborg Side
data.meta_description: The Vyborg Side is a 1939 Soviet drama movie directed by Grigori Kozintsev and Leonid Trauberg. It stars Boris Chirkov, Valentina Kibardina, and Mikhail Zharov.
data.text: The Vyborg Side (Russian: Выборгская сторона) is a 1939 Soviet drama movie directed by Grigori Kozintsev and Leonid Trauberg.[1][2] It stars Boris Chirkov, Valentina Kibardina, and Mikhail Zharov.
